      "source": [
        "# [BLOCK 01] CANONICAL PRDF WORLD ENGINE (DAILY + INTRA-DAY) WITH HAVEN\n",
        "\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "\n",
        "def seasonal(day, period_days=365, amp=0.6, phase=0.0):\n",
        "    return 1.0 + amp * np.sin(2.0 * np.pi * (day / period_days) + phase)\n",
        "\n",
        "def diurnal(step, steps_per_day=200, amp=1.0, phase=-np.pi/2):\n",
        "    raw = 1.0 + amp * np.sin(2.0 * np.pi * (step / steps_per_day) + phase)\n",
        "    return max(0.0, raw)\n",
        "\n",
        "def gates(day, step, steps_per_day,\n",
        "          seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "          seasonal_wet_amp=0.3, diurnal_wet_amp=0.2,\n",
        "          refuge=1.0):\n",
        "    uv = seasonal(day, amp=seasonal_uv_amp) * diurnal(step, steps_per_day, amp=diurnal_uv_amp) * refuge\n",
        "    wet = seasonal(day, amp=seasonal_wet_amp, phase=np.pi/2) * diurnal(step, steps_per_day, amp=diurnal_wet_amp)\n",
        "    return wet, uv\n",
        "\n",
        "def simulate_world_prdf(\n",
        "    world_name,\n",
        "    days=365,\n",
        "    steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "    # Forcing\n",
        "    seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "    seasonal_wet_amp=0.3, diurnal_wet_amp=0.2,\n",
        "    refuge=1.0,\n",
        "    # Temperature proxies\n",
        "    temp_kinetics=1.0,\n",
        "    temp_damage=1.0,\n",
        "    # Couplings\n",
        "    alpha_FR=1.2,\n",
        "    alpha_RP=0.8,\n",
        "    alpha_PD=0.6,\n",
        "    # Haven (proto-matrix) strength\n",
        "    haven_strength=0.5,\n",
        "    # Basal trickles\n",
        "    sF=0.02, sR=1e-6, sP=1e-8, sD=1e-10,\n",
        "    # Damage base rates\n",
        "    kF=0.01, kR=0.02, kP=0.015, kD=0.01,\n",
        "    # Caps\n",
        "    KF=5.0, KR=5.0, KP=5.0, KD=5.0,\n",
        "    # Service allocation\n",
        "    bind_strength=2.0,\n",
        "    # Seeds\n",
        "    F0=0.1, R0=1e-4, P0=1e-6, D0=1e-8,\n",
        "    # Intra-day sampling\n",
        "    sample_day=100\n",
        "):\n",
        "    dt = 1.0 / steps_per_day\n",
        "\n",
        "    F = float(F0); R = float(R0); P = float(P0); D = float(D0)\n",
        "    daily = []\n",
        "    intra = {\"world\": [], \"day\": [], \"step\": [], \"wet\": [], \"uv\": [], \"F\": [], \"R\": [], \"P\": [], \"D\": []}\n",
        "\n",
        "    for day in range(days):\n",
        "        for step in range(steps_per_day):\n",
        "            wet, uv = gates(day, step, steps_per_day,\n",
        "                            seasonal_uv_amp=seasonal_uv_amp, diurnal_uv_amp=diurnal_uv_amp,\n",
        "                            seasonal_wet_amp=seasonal_wet_amp, diurnal_wet_amp=diurnal_wet_amp,\n",
        "                            refuge=refuge)\n",
        "\n",
        "            # Haven: concentration + shelter\n",
        "            concentration_boost = 1.0 + haven_strength * P\n",
        "            shelter = max(0.0, 1.0 - haven_strength * P)\n",
        "\n",
        "            # Damage scales with UV and temp_damage\n",
        "            kF_eff = (kF * temp_damage) * uv * shelter\n",
        "            kR_eff = (kR * temp_damage) * uv * shelter\n",
        "            kP_eff = (kP * temp_damage) * uv * shelter\n",
        "            kD_eff = (kD * temp_damage) * uv * shelter\n",
        "\n",
        "            # Formation scales with wet and temp_kinetics\n",
        "            formF = (sF * temp_kinetics) * wet * concentration_boost\n",
        "            formR = (sR * temp_kinetics) * wet * concentration_boost\n",
        "            formP = (sP * temp_kinetics) * wet * concentration_boost\n",
        "            formD = (sD * temp_kinetics) * wet * concentration_boost\n",
        "\n",
        "            # F\n",
        "            F = max(0.0, F + (formF * (1.0 - F / KF) - kF_eff * F) * dt)\n",
        "\n",
        "            # Service allocation\n",
        "            demand = bind_strength * (R + P + D)\n",
        "            F_bound = min(F, demand)\n",
        "\n",
        "            # R\n",
        "            gR = formR + alpha_FR * F_bound * wet * R * (1.0 - R / KR)\n",
        "            R = max(0.0, R + (gR - kR_eff * R) * dt)\n",
        "\n",
        "            # P (proto-matrix)\n",
        "            gP = formP + alpha_RP * R * wet * (1.0 - P / KP)\n",
        "            P = max(0.0, P + (gP - kP_eff * P) * dt)\n",
        "\n",
        "            # D\n",
        "            gD = formD + alpha_PD * P * wet * (1.0 - D / KD)\n",
        "            D = max(0.0, D + (gD - kD_eff * D) * dt)\n",
        "\n",
        "            if day == sample_day:\n",
        "                intra[\"world\"].append(world_name)\n",
        "                intra[\"day\"].append(day)\n",
        "                intra[\"step\"].append(step)\n",
        "                intra[\"wet\"].append(wet)\n",
        "                intra[\"uv\"].append(uv)\n",
        "                intra[\"F\"].append(F)\n",
        "                intra[\"R\"].append(R)\n",
        "                intra[\"P\"].append(P)\n",
        "                intra[\"D\"].append(D)\n",
        "\n",
        "        daily.append({\"world\": world_name, \"day\": day, \"F\": F, \"R\": R, \"P\": P, \"D\": D})\n",
        "\n",
        "    return pd.DataFrame(daily), pd.DataFrame(intra)"
      ],

        "# [BLOCK 06 but inserts after block01 to bring cyclic reentry] PRDF ENGINE v2: FLOW-THROUGH (WASHOUT) + CYCLIC RE-ENTRY (RECYCLE)\n",
        "\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "\n",
        "def simulate_world_prdf_flow(\n",
        "    world_name,\n",
        "    days=365,\n",
        "    steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Forcing\n",
        "    seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "    seasonal_wet_amp=0.3, diurnal_wet_amp=0.2,\n",
        "    refuge=1.0,\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Temperature proxies\n",
        "    temp_kinetics=1.0,\n",
        "    temp_damage=1.0,\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Couplings\n",
        "    alpha_FR=1.2,\n",
        "    alpha_RP=0.8,\n",
        "    alpha_PD=0.6,\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Haven (proto-matrix)\n",
        "    haven_strength=0.5,\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Basal trickles\n",
        "    sF=0.02, sR=1e-6, sP=1e-8, sD=1e-10,\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Damage base rates\n",
        "    kF=0.01, kR=0.02, kP=0.015, kD=0.01,\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Caps\n",
        "    KF=5.0, KR=5.0, KP=5.0, KD=5.0,\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Service allocation\n",
        "    bind_strength=2.0,\n",
        "\n",
        "    # FLOW-THROUGH / POOL\n",
        "    washout_rate=0.0,         # per-day fraction removed (0=pool; >0=river/flow-through)\n",
        "    washout_on_uv=0.0,        # extra washout during UV (e.g. photobleaching + flushing)\n",
        "    washout_on_wet=0.0,       # extra washout during wet (e.g. tides flushing)\n",
        "\n",
        "    # CYCLIC RE-ENTRY (RECYCLE)\n",
        "    recycle_fraction=0.0,     # fraction of today's losses recycled back into F (precursor pool)\n",
        "    recycle_targets=(\"F\",),   # could later expand to include R precursors etc.\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Seeds\n",
        "    F0=0.1, R0=1e-4, P0=1e-6, D0=1e-8,\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Intra-day sampling\n",
        "    sample_day=100\n",
        "):\n",
        "    dt = 1.0 / steps_per_day\n",
        "\n",
        "    F = float(F0); R = float(R0); P = float(P0); D = float(D0)\n",
        "    daily = []\n",
        "    intra = {\"world\": [], \"day\": [], \"step\": [], \"wet\": [], \"uv\": [], \"F\": [], \"R\": [], \"P\": [], \"D\": []}\n",
        "\n",
        "    for day in range(days):\n",
        "        # Track daily losses to enable recycle\n",
        "        loss_F_day = 0.0\n",
        "        loss_R_day = 0.0\n",
        "        loss_P_day = 0.0\n",
        "        loss_D_day = 0.0\n",
        "\n",
        "        for step in range(steps_per_day):\n",
        "            wet, uv = gates(day, step, steps_per_day,\n",
        "                            seasonal_uv_amp=seasonal_uv_amp, diurnal_uv_amp=diurnal_uv_amp,\n",
        "                            seasonal_wet_amp=seasonal_wet_amp, diurnal_wet_amp=diurnal_wet_amp,\n",
        "                            refuge=refuge)\n",
        "\n",
        "            # Haven: concentration + shelter\n",
        "            concentration_boost = 1.0 + haven_strength * P\n",
        "            shelter = max(0.0, 1.0 - haven_strength * P)\n",
        "\n",
        "            # Damage (UV) losses per unit time\n",
        "            kF_eff = (kF * temp_damage) * uv * shelter\n",
        "            kR_eff = (kR * temp_damage) * uv * shelter\n",
        "            kP_eff = (kP * temp_damage) * uv * shelter\n",
        "            kD_eff = (kD * temp_damage) * uv * shelter\n",
        "\n",
        "            # Formation (wet) rates per unit time\n",
        "            formF = (sF * temp_kinetics) * wet * concentration_boost\n",
        "            formR = (sR * temp_kinetics) * wet * concentration_boost\n",
        "            formP = (sP * temp_kinetics) * wet * concentration_boost\n",
        "            formD = (sD * temp_kinetics) * wet * concentration_boost\n",
        "\n",
        "            # --- Apply formation + damage (explicitly track loss) ---\n",
        "            # F\n",
        "            F_gain = formF * (1.0 - F / KF) * dt\n",
        "            F_loss = kF_eff * F * dt\n",
        "            F = max(0.0, F + F_gain - F_loss)\n",
        "            loss_F_day += F_loss\n",
        "\n",
        "            # Service allocation\n",
        "            demand = bind_strength * (R + P + D)\n",
        "            F_bound = min(F, demand)\n",
        "\n",
        "            # R\n",
        "            R_gain = (formR + alpha_FR * F_bound * wet * R * (1.0 - R / KR)) * dt\n",
        "            R_loss = kR_eff * R * dt\n",
        "            R = max(0.0, R + R_gain - R_loss)\n",
        "            loss_R_day += R_loss\n",
        "\n",
        "            # P\n",
        "            P_gain = (formP + alpha_RP * R * wet * (1.0 - P / KP)) * dt\n",
        "            P_loss = kP_eff * P * dt\n",
        "            P = max(0.0, P + P_gain - P_loss)\n",
        "            loss_P_day += P_loss\n",
        "\n",
        "            # D\n",
        "            D_gain = (formD + alpha_PD * P * wet * (1.0 - D / KD)) * dt\n",
        "            D_loss = kD_eff * D * dt\n",
        "            D = max(0.0, D + D_gain - D_loss)\n",
        "            loss_D_day += D_loss\n",
        "\n",
        "            # Optional: intra-day sample\n",
        "            if day == sample_day:\n",
        "                intra[\"world\"].append(world_name)\n",
        "                intra[\"day\"].append(day)\n",
        "                intra[\"step\"].append(step)\n",
        "                intra[\"wet\"].append(wet)\n",
        "                intra[\"uv\"].append(uv)\n",
        "                intra[\"F\"].append(F)\n",
        "                intra[\"R\"].append(R)\n",
        "                intra[\"P\"].append(P)\n",
        "                intra[\"D\"].append(D)\n",
        "\n",
        "            # Optional: continuous washout (per time step)\n",
        "            # Interpret washout_rate as per-day fraction removed; distribute across day\n",
        "            wash_base = washout_rate * dt\n",
        "            wash_extra = 0.0\n",
        "            wash_extra += washout_on_uv * uv * dt\n",
        "            wash_extra += washout_on_wet * wet * dt\n",
        "            wash = wash_base + wash_extra\n",
        "\n",
        "            if wash > 0:\n",
        "                # remove a fraction of each pool (flow-through)\n",
        "                F_w = wash * F\n",
        "                R_w = wash * R\n",
        "                P_w = wash * P\n",
        "                D_w = wash * D\n",
        "                F = max(0.0, F - F_w)\n",
        "                R = max(0.0, R - R_w)\n",
        "                P = max(0.0, P - P_w)\n",
        "                D = max(0.0, D - D_w)\n",
        "\n",
        "                # washout counts as \"loss\" that can be recycled (if you want)\n",
        "                loss_F_day += F_w\n",
        "                loss_R_day += R_w\n",
        "                loss_P_day += P_w\n",
        "                loss_D_day += D_w\n",
        "\n",
        "        # --- Daily recycle (cyclic re-entry) ---\n",
        "        if recycle_fraction > 0:\n",
        "            recycled = recycle_fraction * (loss_F_day + loss_R_day + loss_P_day + loss_D_day)\n",
        "\n",
        "            if \"F\" in recycle_targets:\n",
        "                F = min(KF, F + recycled)\n",
        "            # (Later we can add explicit precursor pools for R/P/D if desired.)\n",
        "\n",
        "        daily.append({\"world\": world_name, \"day\": day, \"F\": F, \"R\": R, \"P\": P, \"D\": D})\n",
        "\n",
        "    return pd.DataFrame(daily), pd.DataFrame(intra)"
      ],

        "# [BLOCK 02] RUN THREE WORLDS + SAVE DAILY + INTRA-DAY TO DRIVE\n",
        "\n",
        "WORLDS = [\n",
        "    dict(world_name=\"tidal_pool\", refuge=1.0, seasonal_uv_amp=0.7, diurnal_uv_amp=1.2, seasonal_wet_amp=0.6, diurnal_wet_amp=0.4, temp_kinetics=1.0, temp_damage=1.0),\n",
        "    dict(world_name=\"cave\",       refuge=0.15, seasonal_uv_amp=0.2, diurnal_uv_amp=0.2, seasonal_wet_amp=0.2, diurnal_wet_amp=0.1, temp_kinetics=0.9, temp_damage=0.6),\n",
        "    dict(world_name=\"hot_spring\", refuge=0.6, seasonal_uv_amp=0.5, diurnal_uv_amp=0.8, seasonal_wet_amp=0.4, diurnal_wet_amp=0.2, temp_kinetics=1.5, temp_damage=1.3),\n",
        "]\n",
        "\n",
        "ENGINE = dict(alpha_FR=1.2, alpha_RP=0.8, alpha_PD=0.6, haven_strength=0.5, bind_strength=2.0)\n",
        "\n",
        "dfs = []\n",
        "intras = []\n",
        "for w in WORLDS:\n",
        "    df_d, df_i = simulate_world_prdf(**w, **ENGINE)\n",
        "    dfs.append(df_d)\n",
        "    intras.append(df_i)\n",
        "\n",
        "df_all = pd.concat(dfs, ignore_index=True)\n",
        "df_intra = pd.concat(intras, ignore_index=True)\n",
        "\n",
        "daily_path = DATA_DIR / \"PRDF_three_worlds_daily.csv\"\n",
        "intra_path = DATA_DIR / \"PRDF_three_worlds_intra_day.csv\"\n",
        "\n",
        "df_all.to_csv(daily_path, index=False)\n",
        "df_intra.to_csv(intra_path, index=False)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"Saved:\", daily_path)\n",
        "print(\"Saved:\", intra_path)"

        "# [BLOCK 03] PLOT DAILY (LINEAR + LOG) AND SAVE PNGs\n",
        "\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "\n",
        "df_all = pd.read_csv(DATA_DIR / \"PRDF_three_worlds_daily.csv\")\n",
        "\n",
        "def plot_daily(var, log=False):\n",
        "    plt.figure()\n",
        "    for w in df_all[\"world\"].unique():\n",
        "        s = df_all[df_all[\"world\"] == w]\n",
        "        y = s[var].values\n",
        "        if log:\n",
        "            y = np.maximum(y, 1e-12)\n",
        "        plt.plot(s[\"day\"].values, y, label=w)\n",
        "    if log:\n",
        "        plt.yscale(\"log\")\n",
        "    plt.xlabel(\"Day\")\n",
        "    plt.ylabel(var + (\" (log)\" if log else \"\"))\n",
        "    plt.title(f\"{var} across worlds\" + (\" (log)\" if log else \" (linear)\"))\n",
        "    plt.grid(True, linestyle=\":\", linewidth=0.5)\n",
        "    plt.legend(loc=\"upper right\")\n",

        "# [BLOCK 04] PLOT INTRA-DAY (TIDAL POOL) AND SAVE PNGs\n",
        "\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "\n",
        "df_intra = pd.read_csv(DATA_DIR / \"PRDF_three_worlds_intra_day.csv\")\n",
        "tidal = df_intra[df_intra[\"world\"] == \"tidal_pool\"].copy()\n",
        "\n",
        "x = tidal[\"step\"].values\n",
        "\n",
        "# Gates\n",
        "plt.figure()\n",
        "plt.plot(x, tidal[\"wet\"].values, label=\"wet\")\n",
        "plt.plot(x, tidal[\"uv\"].values, label=\"uv\")\n",
        "plt.title(\"tidal_pool intra-day gates\")\n",
        "plt.xlabel(\"Step\")\n",
        "plt.ylabel(\"gate\")\n",
        "plt.grid(True, linestyle=\":\", linewidth=0.5)\n",
        "plt.legend(loc=\"upper right\")\n",
        "out = FIG_DIR / \"tidal_intra_gates.png\"\n",
        "plt.savefig(out, dpi=300, bbox_inches=\"tight\")\n",
        "plt.show()\n",
        "print(\"Saved:\", out)\n",
        "\n",
        "def plot_intra_var(var, log=False):\n",
        "    plt.figure()\n",
        "    y = tidal[var].values\n",
        "    if log:\n",
        "        y = np.maximum(y, 1e-12)\n",
        "        plt.yscale(\"log\")\n",
        "    plt.plot(x, y, label=var)\n",
        "    plt.title(f\"tidal_pool intra-day {var}\" + (\" (log)\" if log else \" (linear)\"))\n",
        "    plt.xlabel(\"Step\")\n",
        "    plt.ylabel(var)\n",
        "    plt.grid(True, linestyle=\":\", linewidth=0.5)\n",
        "    plt.legend(loc=\"upper right\")\n",
        "    out = FIG_DIR / f\"tidal_intra_{var}_{'log' if log else 'linear'}.png\"\n",
        "    plt.savefig(out, dpi=300, bbox_inches=\"tight\")\n",
        "    plt.show()\n",
        "    print(\"Saved:\", out)\n",
        "\n",
        "for var in [\"F\",\"R\",\"P\",\"D\"]:\n",
        "    plot_intra_var(var, log=False)\n",
        "    plot_intra_var(var, log=True)"
      ],

        "# [BLOCK 05] METRICS: LAG + PLATEAU TIMES (SAVE CSV)\n",
        "\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "\n",
        "df_all = pd.read_csv(DATA_DIR / \"PRDF_three_worlds_daily.csv\")\n",
        "\n",
        "KR = 5.0; KP = 5.0; KD = 5.0  # must match ENGINE caps inside simulate_world_prdf\n",
        "\n",
        "def t_to(arr, thr):\n",
        "    idx = np.where(arr >= thr)[0]\n",
        "    return int(idx[0]) if len(idx) else np.nan\n",
        "\n",
        "rows = []\n",
        "for w in df_all[\"world\"].unique():\n",
        "    s = df_all[df_all[\"world\"] == w].sort_values(\"day\")\n",
        "    R = s[\"R\"].values; P = s[\"P\"].values; D = s[\"D\"].values\n",
        "    rows.append({\n",
        "        \"world\": w,\n",
        "        \"t_R_0.01\": t_to(R, 0.01),\n",
        "        \"t_P_0.01\": t_to(P, 0.01),\n",
        "        \"t_D_0.01\": t_to(D, 0.01),\n",
        "        \"t_R_plateau\": t_to(R, 0.9*KR),\n",
        "        \"t_P_plateau\": t_to(P, 0.9*KP),\n",
        "        \"t_D_plateau\": t_to(D, 0.9*KD),\n",
        "        \"final_R\": float(R[-1]),\n",
        "        \"final_P\": float(P[-1]),\n",
        "        \"final_D\": float(D[-1]),\n",
        "    })\n",
        "\n",
        "metrics = pd.DataFrame(rows).sort_values(\"t_D_0.01\")\n",
        "out = OUT_DIR / \"PRDF_metrics_by_world.csv\"\n",
        "metrics.to_csv(out, index=False)\n",
        "print(metrics.to_string(index=False))\n",
        "print(\"Saved:\", out)"
      ],
